gui.newbie.guide.content1: ▢FF5C3C10Welcome to the Uncharted Waters! Here is the main city.
gui.newbie.guide.content3: ▢FF5C3C10You need enough money to strengthen your battleship.
gui.newbie.guide.content4: ▢FF5C3C10Luckily, you can earn money in a variety of ways on the sea.
gui.newbie.guide.content5: ▢FF5C3C10The easiest way to earn money is fishing and selling what you got to the bussiness man. Different items will be caught in different area of the sea!
gui.newbie.guide.content6: ▢FF5C3C10Take the fishing rod in your hand and click on the fishing button to fish. If there is a fish on the hook, remember to click the finish button to prevent it from running away!
gui.newbie.guide.content7: ▢FF5C3C10There are many reefs on the sea, and you can get money by destroying them with attacking weapons on the bow.
gui.newbie.guide.content8: ▢FF5C3C10Equipped with a ship attack weapon in your backpack, you can attack and gradually destroy reefs once you are near them! The higher the attack ability of the weapon, the faster you destroy reefs! So remember to upgrade your weapons often.
gui.newbie.guide.content9: ▢FF5C3C10You can also spend a certain amount of money on the duel at the area manager, having a battleship duel with other adventurers in the main city duel area.
gui.newbie.guide.content10: ▢FF5C3C10Use your battleship skillfully to destroy enemy ships within a specified time. Win the duel to get more money rewards!
gui.newbie.guide.content11: ▢FF5C3C10Now, I will send you a ship and an attack weapon, weapon should be equipped on the ship, this is the first step to become a sea tyrant!
gui.newbie.guide.content12: ▢FF5C3C10Caution: Sailing and being attacked are durability consumed. When the ship's durability down to zero, you will be sent back to the birth point while losing money.
gui.newbie.guide.content13: ▢FF5C3C10You can buy an identity flag from the ship renovation merchant. Once the flag equipped on your ship, you will get the corresponding identity. There are three kinds of identities in the game.
gui.newbie.guide.content14: ▢FF5C3C10By equipping your ship with the fisherman's flag, you will become a fisherman! This identity can increase the efficiency of fishing, and catch valuable items that other identities can't catch!
gui.newbie.guide.content15: ▢FF5C3C10By equipping your ship with a pirate flag, you will become a pirate! Killing is your instinct. You can get extra money rewards every time you destroy other players' ships, which will also increase your evil points.
gui.newbie.guide.content16: ▢FF5C3C10By equipping your ship with a naval flag, you will become a naval! You need to maintain order on the sea. Killing players with high evil values will receive extra money rewards, but your evil points will not increase. But killing players with no evil value will double yours.
gui.newbie.guide.content17: ▢FF5C3C10Not only flags, from the ship renovation merchant, you can also buy Wing and pushers for your ship to create a unique super battleship!
gui.newbie.guide.content18: ▢FF5C3C10There are many precious relics that have existed for a long time in the sea. Near the sea crystal lamps, there will be an occupation button, and you can occupy relic by clicking the button! It will bring you a continuous money reward!
gui.newbie.guide.content19: ▢FF5C3C10If someone else has taken over the relic, you can destroy it by hand! Put your flag to occupy it!
gui.newbie.guide.content20: ▢FF5C3C10There are unmanned ghost ships on the surface of the sea, and destroying them can get a lot of money at once!
gui.newbie.guide.content21: ▢FF5C3C10There are many unknown sea monsters hidden in the sea. Kiill them to get rich and unimaginable money rewards!
gui.newbie.guide.content22: ▢FF5C3C10It seems there are some good things hidden with the octopus, kill them to get surprises!
gui.newbie.guide.content23: ▢FF5C3C10Occasionally, there will be some reward points on the sea, as long as you get there, you can get rewards!
gui.newbie.guide.content24: ▢FF5C3C10Now, go and embrace the sea! Don't worry about forgetting these instructions, you can click the question mark button on the screen to remind yourself at any time!
